		<section class="page-banner-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>Plastering</h1>
				<ul id="breadcrumbs" class="page-depth"><li><a rel="v:url" property="v:title" href="https://ljvconstruction.co.uk//">Home</a></li><li class="active">Plastering</li></ul>			</div>
		</section>
		<!-- End page-banner section -->

		<!-- blog section 
			================================================== -->
		<section class="blog-section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-8">
												<div class="blog-box">

							<div class="blog-post single-post">
																<div class="post-content-text">
									
									 <p>We carry out all types of plastering and dry lining works to accommodate your needs.<br />
Skim finish on board or sand and cement is the most commonly used plasterwork on the internal surfaces of a building, with either roughcast or smooth render to the external surfaces, also used is K Render which comes in a variety of colours.<br />
We also carry out the more traditional method of using hydraulic lime for rendering for all internal or external finishes.</p>
